#########################################
### AUTENTICAÇÃO
#########################################

### 1. Registrar novo usuário (PRIMEIRO PASSO)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@example.com",
  "name": "Nome do Usuário",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### 2. Fazer login e obter token JWT (SEGUNDO PASSO)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@example.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### 3. Usar o token nas requisições (copie o accessToken da resposta acima)
### Substitua {token} pelo token retornado no login
###
### Exemplo: Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

#########################################
### CLIENTES (Requerem autenticação)
#########################################

### Listar todos os clientes
GET http://localhost:3000/clients
Authorization: Bearer {cole-aqui-o-token-jwt}

### Criar um novo cliente
POST http://localhost:3000/clients
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {cole-aqui-o-token-jwt}

{
  "name": "Acme Inc."
}

### Criar outro cliente
POST http://localhost:3000/clients
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {cole-aqui-o-token-jwt}

{
  "name": "Cliente B"
}

### Buscar cliente por ID (substitua {id} pelo ID real)
GET http://localhost:3000/clients/{id}
Authorization: Bearer {cole-aqui-o-token-jwt}

### Atualizar cliente (substitua {id} pelo ID real)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/clients/{id}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {cole-aqui-o-token-jwt}

{
  "name": "Acme Inc. (Atualizado)"
}

### Deletar cliente (substitua {id} pelo ID real)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/clients/{id}
Authorization: Bearer {cole-aqui-o-token-jwt}

